<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10490] TestMapFile and TestBloomMapFile leak file descriptors.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10490</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Multiple tests in &lt;tt&gt;TestMapFile&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;TestBloomMapFile&lt;/tt&gt; open files but don&apos;t close them.  On Windows, the leaked file descriptors cause subsequent tests to fail, because file locks are still held while trying to delete the test data directory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12707832">HADOOP-10490</key>
            <summary>TestMapFile and TestBloomMapFile leak file descriptors.</summary>
